WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.700
Shunday qilib, ushbu mashq bizdan kamalak shaklini chizish uchun ushbu ranglar ro‘yxatidan foydalanishni so‘radi.

00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:09.030
Ushbu videoda men

00:00:09.030 --> 00:00:11.670
har ikki tomon boshqacha rangda bo‘lgan oltiburchak chizishni ko‘rsataman.

00:00:11.670 --> 00:00:15.690
Ushbu ro‘yxatda olti tomon borligi va oltiburchak va oltita rang mavjudligi sababli

00:00:15.690 --> 00:00:18.040
har bir tomon uchun bitta rang bo‘ladi.

00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:21.930
Biz qilishimiz kerak bo‘lgan birinchi narsa yangi turtle yaratish uchun kod qo‘shishdir.

00:00:21.930 --> 00:00:24.510
Keyin oltiburchak chizish uchun kodni yozishimiz mumkin.

00:00:24.510 --> 00:00:26.700
Biz hozirgacha oldingi dars shunga o‘xshash narsani qildik,

00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:29.915
lekin biz uni hali kamalak rangiga aylantirmadik.

00:00:29.915 --> 00:00:33.530
Men biron bir yangi narsani sinab ko‘rganimda va buni qanday qilish kerakligini aniq bilmaganimda,

00:00:33.530 --> 00:00:36.710
men ​​ko‘pincha qanday qilishni juda yaxshi biladigan qismlardan boshlayman,

00:00:36.710 --> 00:00:40.110
keyin yangi narsaga qarab bosqichma-bosqich davom etaman.

00:00:40.110 --> 00:00:43.520
Xullas, hozirda men kamalakning qismi haqida tashvishlanmayman.

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:46.090
Men shunchaki oltiburchak chizishdan boshlamoqchiman.

00:00:46.090 --> 00:00:48.845
Buning uchun men sikldan foydalanmoqchiman.

00:00:48.845 --> 00:00:51.470
oltiburchak olti qirrali

00:00:51.470 --> 00:00:53.905
Men olti marta aylanib chiqaman.

00:00:53.905 --> 00:00:57.285
Men buni shunga o‘xshash oltita elementdan iborat ro‘yxat yordamida amalga oshirishim mumkin.

00:00:57.285 --> 00:00:59.385
Har safar sikl ishlaganda

00:00:59.385 --> 00:01:01.130
Men turtle ni oldinga olib boraman

00:01:01.130 --> 00:01:04.280
100 piksel, bu oltiburchak burchaklardan biri bo‘ladi.

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:06.195
Keyin burilish kerak.

00:01:06.195 --> 00:01:07.460
Oldin ko‘rganimizdek,

00:01:07.460 --> 00:01:10.550
har qanday oddiy ko‘pburchak uchun burilish burchagini

00:01:10.550 --> 00:01:13.970
360 gradusni ko‘pburchak tomonlari soniga bo‘lish orqali olishimiz mumkin.

00:01:13.970 --> 00:01:16.925
Uch yuz oltmish oltiga bo‘lingan holda 60 ga teng

00:01:16.925 --> 00:01:20.410
shuning uchun men turtle ni 60 gradusga o‘ngga buraman.

00:01:20.410 --> 00:01:24.320
Shunday qilib, ushbu nuqtada biz oltiburchak chizadigan kodga ega bo‘lishimiz kerak.

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:26.930
kodimda nima bo‘lgan taqdirda ham u ishlashi kerak

00:01:26.930 --> 00:01:29.620
va ko‘rinadigan natijalarga ega bo‘lishi kerak deb o‘ylayman,

00:01:29.620 --> 00:01:32.905
Men buni kutganimdek ishlashiga ishonch hosil qilish uchun uni sinab ko‘rishni yaxshi ko‘raman.

00:01:32.905 --> 00:01:36.680
U ishlayotganda har xil kichik xatolarga duch kelishim mumkin edi,

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:39.350
va... u oltiburchak chizganga o‘xshaydi.

00:01:39.350 --> 00:01:43.320
Bunday ingichka qora chiziqdan foydalanganligi sababli buni ko‘rish juda qiyin.

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:45.870
Shunday qilib, bitta kichik narsani o‘zgartirib,

00:01:45.870 --> 00:01:49.330
chiziqni qalinlashtirish mumkin.

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:53.545
Endi rangni o‘zgartirish haqida o‘ylashimiz kerak.

00:01:53.545 --> 00:01:58.265
Dastlab, avvalgiday bitta rangni belgilashdan boshlayman.

00:01:58.265 --> 00:02:01.775
Menga, oltiburchak markazlashmagani yoqmayapti.

00:02:01.775 --> 00:02:03.725
Bu o‘ng tomonga surilgan.

00:02:03.725 --> 00:02:07.810
Shunday qilib, men turtle ni chizishni boshlashdan oldin biroz orqaga qilaman.

00:02:07.810 --> 00:02:11.590
Endi turtle ni shaklni chizib bo‘lganidan keyin yashiraman

00:02:11.590 --> 00:02:15.820
kichik o‘q shaklimizni buzmasligi uchun.

00:02:16.180 --> 00:02:19.105
Shunday qilib, endi har sikldan o‘tishda rang o‘zgartirishiga

00:02:19.105 --> 00:02:22.165
 qanday erishish mumkinligi haqida o‘ylashimiz kerak

00:02:22.165 --> 00:02:25.305
va biz bu ranglar ro‘yxatidan foydalanishni xohlaymiz.

00:02:25.305 --> 00:02:28.420
Aniqrog‘i, biz har safar sikldan o‘tganda ushbu 

00:02:28.420 --> 00:02:32.190
ro‘yxatdagi ranglarning boshqasidan foydalanishimiz kerak.

00:02:32.190 --> 00:02:35.380
Bunda go‘yamiz bu sikl o‘zgaruvchisidan foydalanishdir.

00:02:35.380 --> 00:02:38.825
Hozirda bizda side sikl o‘zgaruvchisi bor,

00:02:38.825 --> 00:02:40.620
va siklda har safar

00:02:40.620 --> 00:02:43.100
ushbu o‘zgaruvchiga ushbu ro‘yxatdan raqam beriladi.

00:02:43.100 --> 00:02:44.490
Birdan oltigacha.

00:02:44.490 --> 00:02:46.750
Ammo biz bu raqamlar bilan hech narsa qilmayapmiz.

00:02:46.750 --> 00:02:48.935
Biz shunchaki oltitasi borligidan foydalanmoqdamiz.

00:02:48.935 --> 00:02:54.090
Biroq, bu kamalak ranglari ro‘yxatida, shuningdek, oltita element mavjud.

00:02:54.090 --> 00:02:59.135
Shunday qilib, biz raqamlar ro‘yxatimizni ushbu ranglar ro‘yxati bilan almashtirishimiz mumkin,

00:02:59.135 --> 00:03:01.480
va bizning dasturimiz aslida nima qilayotganini qilaverishi kerak.

00:03:01.480 --> 00:03:04.950
U avvalgidek oltiburchak shaklni chizishi kerak.

00:03:04.950 --> 00:03:08.885
Endi, ushbu ro‘yxatdagi har bir narsa rangga ega bo‘lganligi sababli,

00:03:08.885 --> 00:03:13.295
Men o‘zgaruvchining nomini yon tomondan yoqimli rangga o‘zgartiraman.

00:03:13.295 --> 00:03:16.550
Men buni shunchaki rang emas, balki yoqimli rang deb nomlashim sababi

00:03:16.550 --> 00:03:19.515
uni rang usuli bilan adashtirishni xohlamayman.

00:03:19.515 --> 00:03:21.910
Endi har safar sikl ishlaganda,

00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:25.820
yoqimli rang o‘zgaruvchisi ro‘yxatdan boshqa rangni oladi.

00:03:25.820 --> 00:03:28.710
Avval qizil, keyin zarg‘aldoq, keyin sariq va hokazo.

00:03:28.710 --> 00:03:31.670
Ammo biz hali ham bu ranglar bilan hech narsa qilmayapmiz.

00:03:31.670 --> 00:03:33.040
Shunday qilib, bizning kod ishlaganda,

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:36.230
biz shunchaki qizil oltiburchakga ega bo‘lamiz va bizga kerak bo‘lgan narsa endi

00:03:36.230 --> 00:03:42.840
Bu rangni shu rang o‘zgaruvchisi asosida belgilashdir.

00:03:43.230 --> 00:03:46.320
Endi har safar sikl ishlaganda,

00:03:46.320 --> 00:03:48.500
biz color metodiga

00:03:48.500 --> 00:03:52.355
 oshqa rang uzatamiz,

00:03:52.355 --> 00:03:54.230
va shu tarzda davom etamiz.

00:03:54.230 --> 00:03:55.760
Mana kamalak oltiburchak.

